        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【CES2025】香港創科 VIT 獲 CES 大獎，三軸微型穩定器提升智能電話相機穩定度</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/mgs-2/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mgs-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/mgs-2/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 12:37:07 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[數碼相機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CES2025]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[相機防手震]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1286208</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>香港創科企業在美國拉斯維加斯舉行的 CES 2025 展覽中再創佳績，當中 Vista Innotech（VIT）的三軸微型穩定器（Micro Gimbal Stabilizer, MGS）於影像技術類別中奪得創新獎，成為大中華地區首個獲此殊榮的企業。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286209" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h28-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h28-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h28-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1286220" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010984240-694x479.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="479" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010984240-694x479.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010984240-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>VIT 的三軸 MGS 技術以其精巧設計及卓越性能脫穎而出。產品僅有方糖大小，重量為傳統三軸穩定器的三分之一，體積更縮小至十分之一，具 ±8° 的防手震補償角度，使曝光時間延長至 16 倍，同時生產成本更低。該技術已獲超過 110 項專利保護，應用範圍涵蓋穿戴式相機、安全頭盔及機械人裝置。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286211" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h28-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h28-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h28-2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286210" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h28-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h28-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h28-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286213" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/threeaxismicrogimbal-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/threeaxismicrogimbal-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/threeaxismicrogimbal.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>VIT 行政總裁麥啟邦博士表示，作為大中華首間獲得 CES 創新獎影像技術殊榮的企業，這不僅肯定了 VIT 對技術創新及品質的追求，亦展現了香港企業於全球科技舞台上的潛力。MGS 亦曾獲 2024 年日內瓦發明展銀獎及第二屆城市創科挑戰大獎。</p><h3></h3><figure id="attachment_1286214" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1286214" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1286214" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010983410-694x410.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="410" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010983410-694x410.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010983410-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1286214" class="wp-caption-text">▲在 CES 2025 這個三幅微型影像穩定器獲得創新獎</figcaption></figure><p>資料來源：Unwire.hk, <a href="https://www.ces.tech/ces-innovation-awards/2025/three-axis-micro-gimbal-stabilizer/">CES</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
