            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1286187</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Kodak 與 Barbie 聯手推出 Barbie x Kodak Printomatic，即影即有相機結合復古與創新設計，吸引年輕用戶與 Barbie 迷關注。相機提供 500 萬像素解像度及 ZINK 無墨技術，打印防污、防水及防撕裂的 2×3 吋貼背相片。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286201" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-7-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-7-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-7-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286188" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286199" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/barbiexkodaknews-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/barbiexkodaknews-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/barbiexkodaknews.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>相機採用輕巧設計，方便攜帶，並以 Barbie 經典粉紅色包裝，外型亮眼又實用。內置自動閃光燈與自動對焦功能，讓拍攝者無需經驗亦能捕捉清晰影像。相片除即時打印外，相機還支援 MicroSD 卡儲存，方便用戶保存數碼檔案。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286189" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286190" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286191" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010920h11-3-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>此相機既能作日常拍攝用，也適合成為收藏品。對於喜愛 Barbie 主題產品的用戶而言，這款即影即有相機同時帶來懷舊趣味及現代拍攝體驗。</p><h4>規格</h4><ul><li><strong>解像度</strong>：500 萬像素數碼相機</li><li><strong>打印技術</strong>：ZINK 無墨打印，2×3 吋貼背相片</li><li><strong>功能</strong>：自動閃光燈、自動對焦、MicroSD 存儲支援</li><li><strong>設計</strong>：Barbie 經典粉紅造型</li></ul><h4>售價與供應</h4><p>Barbie x Kodak Printomatic 現已推出，售價 £84.99（約港幣 HK$663）。</p><br /><b>
