        <item>
            <title>【CES2025】LG UltraGear 可彎曲電競熒幕搶鏡，用家一個指令熒幕馬上流暢變彎</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/lg-ultragear-5k2k/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=lg-ultragear-5k2k</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/lg-ultragear-5k2k/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 12:06:46 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流動電腦]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[LG UltraGear]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1286170</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>LG 在 CES 2025 展示他們的最新顯示技術，推出全球首款 5K2K 解像度可彎曲 OLED 顯示器 45GX990A，並贏得三項創新大獎，包括備受矚目的「最佳創新獎」。這款 UltraGear GX9 系列具備的彎曲屏幕設計，可以隨用家需要拉直，或變彎曲（詳細效果可看下面的影片），還融入多項針對遊戲玩家的創新功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286184" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgultrageargx945gx99-694x422.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="422" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgultrageargx945gx99-694x422.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgultrageargx945gx99.jpg 800w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286174" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h53-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h53-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h53-2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><p>LG UltraGear 45GX990A 是一款尺寸達 45 吋、21:9 比例的 OLED 遊戲顯示器，擁有超高 5K2K 解像度（5,120 x 2,160）。用戶可透過按鈕實現屏幕從平面至 900R 曲率之間的自動轉換，適合遊戲玩家在沉浸式遊戲與工作應用之間靈活切換。展示期間，LG 提供了一套紅色按鈕操控裝置，讓參觀者體驗這款屏幕彎曲與平展切換的流暢效果。未來消費版產品將搭載遙控器進行操作。</p><h3></h3><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286173" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h53-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h53-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h53-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286175" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h53-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h53-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h53-3-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><p>這款顯示器採用了 LG 最新 WOLED 技術，提供高亮度、深黑色、豐富色彩及最佳曲率，為遊戲玩家打造更逼真的畫面。同時產品通過低藍光認證，減少長時間遊戲時的眼部負擔。內置的 Dual Mode 功能支持用戶一鍵切換多種畫面比例及更新率配置，適應不同類型的遊戲與內容需求。</p><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286185" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgultrageargx945gx95-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgultrageargx945gx95-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgultrageargx945gx95.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="VID_20250108_102048" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1045315936?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script><br />
資料來源：LG, Unwire.hk</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/lg-ultragear-5k2k/notebook/">【CES2025】LG UltraGear 可彎曲電競熒幕搶鏡，用家一個指令熒幕馬上流暢變彎</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
