        <item>
            <title>【CES2025】Lenovo ThinkBook Plus Gen6，熒幕可捲動、售價 3499 美元起</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/lenovo-thinkbook-plus-gen-6/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=lenovo-thinkbook-plus-gen-6</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/lenovo-thinkbook-plus-gen-6/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 12:03:41 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流動電腦]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CES2025]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[lenovo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Lenovo ThinkBook]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Lenovo ThinkBook Plus Gen6]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1286116</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Lenovo 在 CES2025 展示了他們最新的 ThinkBook Plus Gen6，與傳統筆記型電腦不同，這款全新登場的 ThinkBook Plus Gen6 配備全球首個可捲曲（rollable）熒幕，據悉將在今年首季度推出，預期售價為 $3,499 美元（約港幣 27,223 元）。ThinkBook Plus Gen6 表面上就如一部 14 吋手提電腦，但熒幕可延伸至 16.7 吋，並支援 120 Hz 更新率，用家可以利用更大熒幕靈活辦公。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286137" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo5-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo5-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo5-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo5.jpg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲伸延前為 14 吋熒幕</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286138" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo6-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo6-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo6-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo6.jpg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可伸延至 16.7 吋</p><p>ThinkBook Plus Gen6 最具顛覆性的設計是其可捲曲熒幕。這項突破性技術可根據需求靈活擴展，讓使用者隨時獲得更多操作空間，無論是會議中迅速查找資料、展示文件，還是進行創意設計，這款筆記型電腦都能夠自如應對。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286119" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo1-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo1-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo1-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo1.jpg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊 F12 旁邊按鍵</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286135" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo4-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo4-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo4-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo4.jpg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用家亦可以用手勢延伸熒幕</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286124" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo2-580x580.jpeg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo2-580x580.jpeg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo2-144x144.jpeg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovo2.jpeg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲即可延伸熒幕</p><p>Lenovo ThinkBook Plus Gen6 使用了前所未見的捲動熒幕，其體積和重量並未比傳統手提電腦大或重太多。它重量為 1.63kg，厚度約 1.9cm，保持輕巧與便攜性，讓使用者隨時隨地都能擁有極致的工作效率。ThinkBook Plus Gen 6 內置 Intel Core Ultra 7 CPU、最高可達 32 GB RAM 及 1TB SSD。預期 Lenovo 將會在今年第一季推出 ThinkBook Plus Gen 6，以 $3,499 美元的（約港幣 27,225.11 元）價格上市。預計它將吸引大量追求創新與高效能的商業專業人士與創意工作者，成為他們辦公桌上的新寵。</p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/lenovo-thinkbook-plus-gen-6/notebook/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【CES2025】三星 ✕ 現代智能家居整合到汽車，車芒睇家中監察系統、控制掃地機械人</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/samsung-hyundai-2/wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=samsung-hyundai-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/samsung-hyundai-2/wireless-home/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 11:32:01 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[家居無線]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[samsung]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智能家居]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1286153</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在今屆 CES 2025 消費科技展覽會上，Samsung 展示了在汽車科技領域的最新進展，通過與現代汽車集團的合作，他們將推動 Samsung SmartThings 智能家居與汽車進行深度整合。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1286161 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010972722-694x397.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="397" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010972722-694x397.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010972722-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>關鍵技術與合作</h2><p>SmartThings 平台整合：三星將其 SmartThings 平台擴展到現代電動汽車中，使用戶能夠通過手機控制車輛功能。這包括查找停車位置、根據日程安排充電建議，以及在停電時自動激活電池備份模式，以確保家庭必需品的供電</p><p>Harman 的創新技術：三星子公司 Harman 展示了其「Ready」技術，將汽車轉變為智能夥伴。該技術包括增強現實顯示器和沈浸式音響系統，提升車內體驗。新推出的車載虛擬助手能夠預測駕駛者需求，提供個性化的 AI 互動，幫助駕駛者專注於道路</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286158" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h23-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h23-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h23-3-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286157" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h23-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h23-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h23-2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>AI 驅動的用戶體驗</h2><p>個性化助手：Harman 推出了基於 AI 的車載祕書「Luna」，通過語音和視覺交互為乘客提供自然、直觀的服務。這一助手結合了先進的傳感器技術，可以實時監測駕駛者狀態，從而優化駕駛體驗</p><p>智能座艙體驗：三星繼續與 Harman 合作，為更多車型提供先進的座艙技術，包括多屏幕顯示和影院級音響效果。這些技術不僅提升了娛樂體驗，還增強了安全性和舒適性</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286159" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h22-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h22-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010919h22-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>未來展望</h2><p>三星在 CES 2025 上強調「AI for All」願景，致力於將人工智能融入日常生活的各個方面，包括家庭和汽車。這一戰略提升用戶體驗，為未來的智能出行奠定了基礎。通過不斷創新和合作，三星希望在智能家居和汽車領域建立更緊密的聯繫，為用戶提供更加個性化和便捷的生活方式。</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
